channel.description:
[center][img]http://ohgamers.com/banners/Forgiven.png[/img][/center] [center]I'm releasing this because alot of people who have played my server/seen it wanted a copy, we have moved up to V3 so I have decided I will release it. If you don't like it don't respond. Practice self control. [center][size=14pt]Features:[/size]
Prestige System Summoning Chaotics Vote4Points Added Server Side Multiple Commands Added. (Item DB Search, IP Checker, etc.) Totally Re-Done Slayer & Crafting. Working Ring Of Wealth. Loyalte Titles 100% Custom Loyatle Titles 100% Perfect CB Pkp Slayer Points Multi Barrage Over Powered Curse Glitch Fixed Stable - Held 79 With no DC's. BoB Some Dupes Fixed New Home No Summoning NPCs At Home Castle Wars Base Added. (Flickering Interfaces Need To Be Fixed.) Nooby Clue Scroll System Added Crystal Keys Added. Nomad Soul Wars Bosses Dungeoneering Bosses Safe Cracking Working EXP Lamps. (Various Levels of EXP.) And alot more that I can't think of just check.
[img]http://imageking.us/images/qnhm5.png[/img] [img]http://imageking.us/images/98ZkA.png[/img]
I was taking pictures then my comp decided it didn't want to work anymore so I only got 2. If you don't trust it don't download. (Or be like the smart people and scan files.) But so you can rest your weary hearts here is a virus scan.
Aaron Me Ryan Whoever made this before us.
DOWNLOADSsSsSsS:
The download is a package so yeah... Cache will auto download.
[url=http://dl.dropbox.com/u/58368971/ForgivenX%20Package.rar]ForgivenX - Package - Client + Source.[/url] [url=http://dl.dropbox.com/u/58368971/item.cfg]FIXED ITEM.CFG[/url]
[center]:::::::::EDIT::::::::: Added fixed item.cfg, source should run now. All you need to do is download [url=http://dl.dropbox.com/u/58368971/item.cfg]FIXED ITEM.CFG[/url] and replace the current one in the source with this one.[/center]
